{"tid":1510696,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港法治已死","createTime":"2019-08-27T09:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T09:34:47.000Z","uid":204502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f84993847fca111523343b08a96f54343335b92","tid":1510696,"uid":204502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:30:19.000Z","msg":"【涉機場襲擊環球時報記者 19歲男子申請保釋再被拒】<br />\n<br />\n一名19歲男子涉嫌於本月機場集會期間，包圍及毆打《環球時報》記者付國豪，被控參與非法集結、 傷人、 襲擊致造成身體傷害共3項控罪，案件今日（8月27日）在東區裁判法院再提堂。 <br />\n<br />\n被告今日申請保釋覆核，辯方以被告另外涉及的沙田襲警案獲准保釋為由，希望以1.5萬港元現金擔保，定時到警署報到、不離開香港及遵守宵禁令申請保釋，惟裁判官拒絕，被告繼續還押看管。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指被告涉嫌在8月13至14日期間，在機場一號客運大樓G位通道，與其他不知名人士參與非法集結，作出擾亂秩序的行為，意圖導致任人合理地害怕這樣集結的人會破壞社會安寧，或害怕他們會藉行為，激使其他人破壞社會安寧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點解到而家仲未任何嘅示威係針對法院？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"86b81eead6364a09cfad9b366755fef5c800a688","tid":1510696,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi%2FBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=e62e309f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi%2FBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=8f2e6533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi%2FBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=782e88f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{